The authentication and identity subsystem under
backend/src/lib/identity/ is derived from DRep Talk's src/lib/auth/*,
src/lib/crypto/*, and src/lib/cardano/identity.ts, modified to target
the drep-platform (AWS Lambda) stack.

The DRep directory robustness/UX subsystem under
backend/src/lib/dreps/* and the corresponding handlers + frontend
components is derived from DRep Talk's src/lib/dreps/* (voting-power
concentration math + content-addressed avatar pipeline) and
src/components/DrepConcentration.tsx, modified for drep-platform
(DynamoDB + S3 instead of D1 + R2; AWS Lambda boundary).

